187
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:31,340
This is a good one to talk about with friends or if you're working on a project at work.
这是一个和朋友聊天或工作时讨论项目的好短语。

188
00:08:31,340 --> 00:08:33,300
You say, listen, there's no rush.
你说，听着，不着急。

189
